name: Fred Rispoli

name: Fred Rispoli
tweet: Also, remember DPP can be held to apply BUT OVERCOME if disclosure interests outweigh nondisclosure. The EPA case was a FOIA request, not a request by a company being sued by a govt agency for over $1B. A key difference that Ripple will emphasize and should carry some weight. 4/
